item.description:
Continuing to share tips and tricks using dbatools like the Refresh databases that belongs to availability group using dbatools posted a few days ago, today I will share a way to export the permissions of a login/user at instance/database level and apply them to a new login/user.
The typical request Client: &ldquo;We have a new colleague, can you please grant them the exact same permissions I have?!&rdquo;
A quick note/suggestion that may help minimize your work: If we are talking about a Windows Login, please suggest the use of AD groups to help you (so that you don&rsquo;t need to do this process) and also them (they don&rsquo;t need to make this request).
